programme.desc: Sayang Jangan Sampai Melayang - Tahukah anda, dicatatkan pada tahun , sebanyak lebih 90 bilion harta umat islam yang terbeku tidak dituntut. Harta terkumpul ini saban tahun meningkat kerana waris sentiasa menghadapi kesulitan dalam menjalankan urusan pengurusan harta pusaka. Yang akhirnya, membuatkan waris merasa tidak mahu untuk meneruskan tuntutan. Apakah puncanya? adakah kurang kesedaran berkenaan perancangan harta? atau umat islam tidak mengetahui akan kepentingan pengurusan harta seperti melaksanakan hibah?

programme.title: Dia Menantu Rahsia Ep01
programme.desc: Pertunangan antara Zamer dan Doktor Suraya telah merobek hati Melissa. Pertunangan ini diatur oleh ibu Zamer sendiri. Untuk merawat hatinya yang kecewa, Melissa membawa diri ke Kuala Lumpur. Di sana, dia bertemu dengan Syakir, pemilik Book Cafe tempat Melissa bekerja. Syakir melamar Melissa untuk melindunginya daripada terus menjadi mangsa kekasaran Zamer dan juga untuk mengelakkan permintaan ibunya, Puan Sarah, yang mahu dia menerima cinta Engku Kamelia. Melissa menerima lamaran Syakir semata-mata untuk melarikan diri daripada Zamer yang terus mengejar cintanya. Adakah kebahagiaan dan cinta akan wujud di antara mereka? Dapatkah Melissa diterima dalam keluarga Syakir?

programme.title: Mana Lagi Sedap S1 Ep08
programme.desc: Satu rancangan dimana hos Fizi Ali akan cuba menu istimewa sesebuah restoran dan mencabar dirinya untuk menghasilkan semua masakan restoran tersebut. Menu kali ini adalah Makanan Laut, jadi Mana Lagi Sedap?

programme.title: Suamiku Old School
programme.desc: Alif dan Zureen, berjumpa sewaktu melawat rumah kawan mereka yang baru mendapat cahaya mata. Sikap Alif yang tidak kekok dalam memegang bayi baru lahir telah memberi pandangan pada Zureen yang Alif adalah bapa yang sempurna. Dan Zureen, yang membantu menyiapkan makanan hidangan mereka dirasakan oleh Alif calon sesuai dibuat isteri. Hasil bantuan rakan-rakan mereka berkenalan dan seterusnya berkahwin.

programme.title: Tok Guru S1 Ep06
programme.desc: Gabenor Inggeris risau Malayan Union akan gagal jika orang Melayu terus buat demostrasi. Zaaba, Ahmad Boestamam dan Dr Baharudin Helmi terus berceramah di seluruh pelusuk tanah Melayu memberi penjelasan keburukkan jika orang melayu menerima Malayan Union.

programme.title: Lawak Sentral S2 Ep08

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep05
programme.desc: Lukman masih dihantui mimpi dan kenangan bersama arwah Sarah. Perasaan bersalah atas kematian Sarah tetap mengganggu minda dan emosinya. Dia sering terbayangkan arwah Sarah ketika bersama Farah. Perasaan kelirunya membuatkan Farah sering makan hati.

programme.title: Resepi Rahsia S1 Ep06

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep07
programme.desc: Hope dan Love pergi kepada Faith dengan semua maklumat yang mereka dapat tentang Jose: hartanah yang disita, kes penipuan - semuanya menunjukkan bahawa lelaki yang akan dikahwini oleh ibu mereka tidak mempunyai wang. Faith kecewa, bukan dengan Jose, tetapi dengan anak-anak perempuannya.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep08
programme.desc: Love diberi pilihan: bayar hutangnya, atau dia boleh mengucapkan selamat tinggal kepada anaknya, Noel. Dia tiada pilihan, dan Faith tidak dapat membantunya. Tetapi mungkin seseorang yang lain boleh membantu, jika Love boleh rendahkan egonya dan meminta bantuan Hope.

programme.title: Mr Secret Admirer S1 Ep11
programme.desc: Syed Redza sudah pulih sepenuhnya. Dia sudah boleh berjalan tanpa menggunakan tongkat. Namun dia meminta Datin Fatimah merahsiakan perkara itu dari Lisa.Semasa di Dubai, Zureen berhubung dengan Hj Zailan melalui telefon. Hjh Aminah masih berkecil hati di atas perbuatan Zureen.Di waktu lapang Zureen bersiar-siar di kawasan Bandar seorang diri. Dari situlah Zureen teringat akan kenangan lamanya ketika bersama dengan Syed Redza dan juga Dr Haziq.

programme.title: Ronda - Ronda S2 Ep02

programme.title: You're My Boss

programme.title: Nasi Kerabu Untuk Che Abe Ep06
programme.desc: Selesai kenduri kesyukuran di Kelantan, Tn Badrul mempelawa Mek Yan memperluaskan bisnes dan berbual sehingga larut malam. Faizul hanya mengintai sebab tak mahu terlepas lagi malam "bersama" Shira. Faizul dan Shira pulang ke KL menyambung sesi pengajian. Selepas hantar Shira ke kolej, Faizul berniaga burger. Suatu hari, Shira tergugat dengan kehadiran Sha. Faizul perkenalkan Shira isterinya. Wajah Sha berubah dan hampa. Sha mula menyimpan dendam dan merancang sesuatu untuk dapatkan semula Faizul. Shira mula sangsi mengambil tindakan untuk melihat kejujuran Faizul. Suatu hari Shira terjumpa gincu dalam kereta Faizul.

programme.title: Madu Murni
programme.desc: Cerita berpusat pada Mustaqim (Ammar Zoni), seorang bekas guru mengaji yang kini bekerja sebagai penagih hutang untuk mendapatkan pendapatan yang lebih banyak. Namun, isterinya, Murni (Irish Bella), tidak menyetujui pekerjaan Mustaqim dan enggan menerima wang yang diperolehnya kerana bimbang akan risiko di dunia akhirat. Atas nasihat rakannya, Rojak (Tanta Ginting), Mustaqim memutuskan untuk berkahwin lagi dengan Yati (Aulia Sarah). Filem ini mengisahkan bagaimana Mustaqim cuba mengimbangi kehidupan dengan dua isteri dan pelbagai cabaran yang dihadapinya

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep10
programme.desc: Selepas semua kekecewaan Ezgi menuju ke Bursa untuk membersihkan kepalanya. Nevin dan nal mempersoalkan keadaan Ezgi ini. Walaupun Ezgi menyembunyikan pengalamannya dengan zgr, semuanya terbongkar apabila zgr datang ke Bursa. Permohonan maaf zgr tidak mengubah apa-apa. zgr tidak mempercayainya, yang menyebabkan dia sangat kecewa. Semakin zgr menyendiri, semakin dia merindui Ezgi dan semakin dia menyedari betapa dia menyayanginya. Keadaan fikiran ini mengaktifkan Ozan. Cansu dan Deniz juga kecewa dan menyesal kerana mereka melayan Ezgi dengan salah. Mereka juga bekerjasama dengan Ozan dan cuba membawa Ezgi dan zgr bersama.

programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep11
programme.desc: Ezgi sangat terharu dengan kejutan zgr. Semua kebencian terhadap zgr berlalu. Dalam proses ini, kedua-duanya lebih memahami betapa mereka menghargai satu sama lain. Mereka membuka lembaran baru dalam hubungan mereka, tidak ada lagi tempat untuk pembohongan. Jadi mereka memutuskan untuk memberitahu keluarga mereka bahawa mereka bersama. Nevin menerima perhubungan ini walaupun dia tidak menginginkannya sangat, Sevim pula tidak mahu Ezgi dan zgr bersama. Ezgi mengadakan acara pertamanya di syarikat organisasi yang diupahnya, dan kejutan menantinya di acara ini. Sementara itu, Serdar mengambil tindakan sekali lagi untuk mendapatkan Ezgi, tetapi apabila dia mengetahui bahawa zgr dan Ezgi bersama, dia kecewa dan keadaan ini menjadikannya lebih bercita-cita tinggi.

programme.title: Bawah Payung Awan Ep22
programme.desc: Hanan diserang Zaf setelah skandalnya dengan Dato AJ tersebar. Anita mengungkit tentang Ame kepada Soleiman dan Soleiman tidak mengakui Ame adalah anaknya. Ame merasa kecewa dan sedih setelah mendengar perbualan mereka.

programme.title: The Gadis Ep04
programme.desc: Nad berjaya memujuk Lisa sekali lagi untuk pergi ke KL menjadi Sugarbaby. Lisa keluar dengan seorang Dato yang sanggup berbelanja besar, Lisa mahu mengumpul wang sebanyak mungkin bagi melanjutkan pelajarannya. Malam tersebut Lisa tidak balik rumah, dia berbohong kepada Lina kononnya dia tidur di rumah Rocky. Nad dan Mika merancang untuk menjual Lisa yang masih dara dengan harga yang tinggi bagi menyelesaikan hutang mereka. Mika telah meletakkan dadah dalam minuman Lisa, menyebabkan Lisa tidak sedarkan diri. Rancangan mereka gagal pada malam itu kerana Dato tersebut tidak mampu membayar harga yang tinggi seperti dijanjikan. Apabila Lisa tersedar, Mika berpura-pura mengatakan yang Dato itu cuba mengambil kesempatan kepada Lisa dan Mika telah menyelamatkannya. Lisa terhutang budi dengan Mika. Nad telah membuat satu lagi temujanji dengan seorang Dato bernama Dato Jefri. Melihat Dato Jefri, Lisa terkejut kerana dia tidak seperti Dato sebelum ini. Dato Jefri jauh lebih muda dan kacak, dia seorang duda kematian isteri. Dato Jefri terdengar Lisa masih bersekolah dan akan mengambil peperiksaan SPM

programme.title: Ghost Writer 2
programme.desc: Kejayaan novel keduanya mengharumkan nama Naya. Malangnya dia lebih dilabelkan sebagai psikik daripada penulis. Ini membuatkan Naya geram dan berat hati untuk berhadapan dengan dunia berhantu itu semula. Namun, segalanya berubah apabila bakal suaminya Vino meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba.

programme.title: Bohsia 2: Jalan Kembali
programme.desc: Tasha adalah seorang gadis yang dibesarkan tanpa keluarga dan pendidikan, memaksanya untuk mencari perlindungan di dunia bawah tanah, di kalangan samseng jalanan. Dia tidak lama kemudian menjadi bosan dengan kehidupannya yang tidak bermakna, tetapi jalannya menuju penebusan adalah jalan yang diturap dengan banyak halangan.

programme.title: Janet: Sumpahan Terlarang
programme.desc: Julia adalah gadis Sarawak yang pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk merancang perkahwinannya Farid. Tetapi dia secara tidak sedar menggunakan jepit rambut milik Janet, yang telah menjadi korban ritual dalam membina jambatan.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Encik Bad menjemput Adam, Shah dan Danial menawarkan mereka untuk menangkap lembaga-lembaga di luar. Ini berikutan Muzium Lembaga usaha encik Bad kini sunyi dan tiada pengunjung lagi, berikutan lembaga-lembaga di muzium itu tidak di kemas kini. Setelah berbincang syarat kerja dengan gaji tetap, berbagai elaun, kemudahan insuran dan rawatan serta van baru lalu mereka bertiga bersetuju bekerja dengan encik Bad. Syarat bagi encik Bad dalam sebulan mereka sekurang-kurangnya perlu mendapat 3 lembaga setiap bulan. Mereka juga dibenarkan encik Bad melakukan kerja mereka secara "part time". Kini mereka digelar sebagai pemburu entiti misteri. Sementara itu Shah sempat menemui kekasihnya sedangkan Danial dan Adam terdesak untuk bergerak bagi memulakan tugas. Kemudian mereka berjumpa dengan Prof Din Glamer dan berbincang hal lembaga. Mengikut Prof Din lembaga itu sebenarnya Jin. Tugas pertama mereka telah berjaya menangkap hantu penanggal dan menyerahkan ke encik Bad dan mereka menyedutnya lalu dia berkeadaan terkurung dalam alat penyedut. Di Muzium, encik Bad anggap ianya dilihat kurang menarik. Untuk itu Adam telah sediakan ubat cucuk vaksin yang lembaga penanggal di bawa keluar tetapi setelah dicucuk vaksin lembaga itu akan kaku selama 7 hari. Tugas menyenggelara encik Bad serahkan kepada Kadir. Sementara itu ibu Adam tidak menyukainya bekerja sedemikian.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Detektif Khairul Malik menyimpan sebuah rahsia, yang teman wanitanya, Aisya tidak tahu mengenainya. Perkara menjadi rumit dengan penemuan mayat dua puluh tahun, yang menggerakkan rangkaian kejadian yang membawa maut. Kehidupannya berubah secara mendadak apabila dia bertemu Sofia, gadis yang berkebolehan meramal kematian orang. Apabila dia meramal sebuah tragedi dahsyat, Sofia mendapat perhatian polis dan juga seorang keturunan usahawan insurans ulung, Lokman Nazir. Tertarik dengan bakat unik Sofia, Malik meyakinkan dia untuk bekerja bersamanya untuk menyelamatkan nyawa, tetapi niat baik mereka menyebabkan tragedi. Sementara itu, penghantaran sebuah pita menyebabkan huru-hara dalam hubungan Malik dan Aisya apabila rahsia gelap Aisya mula terungkai.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Pegawai penguatkuasa undang-undang Bunian 444 atau juga dikenali sebagai Black sedang diburu kerana rakan setugasnya seorang penderhaka, 419, telah melarikan diri ke dunia manusia. Menyedari 419 telah menghuni tubuh manusia, Black memutuskan untuk memasuki tubuh Malik untuk bersaing dengannya. Pada mata manusia, 'Malik' telah terselamat daripada kematian dengan menakjubkan sekali dan akibat kejadian itu dia telah hilang ingatan. Dalam pada itu, Sofia mula menyedari yang 'Malik' merupakan buat hatinya semasa kecil dan dia diselubungi rasa bersalah kerana telah meletak Malik dalam situasi bahaya. Namun 'Malik' sekarang ialah Black - biadab, mementingkan diri sendiri dan tekad dengan satu tujuan dalam misinya. Adakah dia akan ingat siapa Sofia sebenarnya? Black mendapati dirinya berdepan dengan pembunuhan yang mengerikan semasa dia cuba mengharungi dunia manusia. Keadaan menjadi lebih rumit apabila seorang lelaki yang penuh misteri muncul dan membayangi setiap gerak-gerinya.

programme.title: Congkak
programme.desc: Kisahnya bermula apabila Kazman serta isterinya Sufiah mengambil keputusan bercuti bersama dua anaknya, Lisa dan Ely di sebuah banglo di tepi tasik. Kazman sudah berjanji dengan seorang kawannya untuk membeli banglo tersebut sebagai persinggahan semasa bercuti. Pelbagai peristiwa pelik berlaku sepanjang perjalan mereka termasuk kehilangan telefon bimbitnya. Setibanya mereka di banglo tersebut, peristiwa yang semakin pelik turut terjadi. Sufiah cuba meyakinkan Kazman untuk keluar dari rumah tersebut tetapi tidak diendahkan. Kazman tetap berkeras untuk membeli rumah tersebut kerana sudah berjanji dengan kawannya. Sufiah sentiasa merasakan ada makhluk sedang memerhatikannya. Salah seorang anak mereka, Lisa setiap malam akan turun ke sebuah bilik gelap untuk bermain congkak dengan seseorang yang hanya boleh dilihat olehnya seorang. Sufiah yang tidak boleh bersabar dengan perkara itu telah membuang congkak tersebut ke dalam tasik. Lisa juga sentiasa bermain di tepi belukar di belakang rumah kerana kawannya tinggal di situ sehingga Kazman perasan Lisa bermain menghadap kubur lama. Pada malam keesokannya, Sufiah dikejutkan lagi dengan bunyi congkak tersebut dari bilik yang sama. Apabila Sufiah pergi melihat, dilihatnya seorang tua sedang bemain congkak tersebut. Semakin lama peristiwa yang berlaku semakin pelik dan menyeramkan sehingga pada malam ketiga kedua-dua anaknya telah hilang dan Sufiah didapati tidur di siling bilik. Pak Tua, penduduk paling lama di kampung itu telah pergi ke rumah tersebut untuk menyelamatkan keluarga Kazman dan mencari Ely dan Lisa. Apakah sejarah sebenar banglo tersebut dan dapatkan Sufiah diselamatkan serta berjayakah Ely dan Lisa ditemui semula.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep 6 Ep6
programme.desc: Haikal terambil botol yang di dalamnya tersimpan peta lokasi dimana batu permata disembunyikan oleh Sohot kawan Salim yang turut terlibat dengan kes rompakan bersama Hariman 5 tahun lalu. Kejadian itu disedari oleh Sohot yang kemudiannya diarah Hariman untuk mendapatkan botol itu semula. Haikal dengan rasa ingin tahu masuk ke dalam hutan bersama Imran untuk menjejaki lokasi seperti di dalam peta tersebut manakala Sohot dan Salim dilihat mengekori mereka

programme.title: Arwah Tumbal Nyai - Part Nyai
programme.desc: Selepas kematian neneknya, Rosmalina merasakan ada makhluk ghaib yang tinggal di rumahnya. Reno, teman lelaki Rosmalina, menyuruhnya berpindah ke rumah lain. Selepas berpindah, ternyata makhluk ghaib itu datang ke pawagam tempat Rosmalina bekerja dan sentiasa mengganasnya. Akhirnya Rosmalina tahu makhluk ghaib yang selalu mengganasnya untuk berhubung rapat dengan Nayla, anak perempuannya. Rosmalina meminta Nayla mengusir makhluk ghaib itu tetapi Nayla marah dan enggan dipisahkan.

programme.title: Den Budak Motor
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Deniel, seorang lelaki yang kecewa ditinggalkan oleh bekas kekasihnya, Sarah disebabkan kesusahan Deniel yang hanya memiliki motor kapcai.

programme.title: Azem 2
programme.desc: Beberapa orang membawa seorang gadis yang dirasuk teruk dengan kotak kayu berkunci untuk menyembuhkannya.

programme.title: Check In Shock
programme.desc: Sekumpulan orang berkumpul di hospital terbiar untuk mengambil bahagian dalam rancangan realiti. Sesiapa yang berjaya bermalam di tempat yang dikatakan berhantu akan memenangi hadiah wang tunai. Apabila malam semakin larut, sesetengah daripada mereka mula mengesyaki bahawa penganjur tidak bercadang untuk membenarkan sesiapa pergi dengan ganjaran. Kebenaran ternyata lebih mengancam apabila roh yang menghantui tempat itu terbukti benar dan mula menyerang mereka.

programme.title: Nemesis
programme.desc: Seorang bekas pesakit psikiatri membalas dendam dan berhasrat untuk menumpaskan sekumpulan penjenayah neraka selepas kemalangan tragis menyaksikan keluarga tercintanya terbunuh.

programme.title: Congkak
programme.desc: Kisahnya bermula apabila Kazman serta isterinya Sufiah mengambil keputusan bercuti bersama dua anaknya, Lisa dan Ely di sebuah banglo di tepi tasik. Kazman sudah berjanji dengan seorang kawannya untuk membeli banglo tersebut sebagai persinggahan semasa bercuti. Pelbagai peristiwa pelik berlaku sepanjang perjalan mereka termasuk kehilangan telefon bimbitnya. Setibanya mereka di banglo tersebut, peristiwa yang semakin pelik turut terjadi. Sufiah cuba meyakinkan Kazman untuk keluar dari rumah tersebut tetapi tidak diendahkan. Kazman tetap berkeras untuk membeli rumah tersebut kerana sudah berjanji dengan kawannya. Sufiah sentiasa merasakan ada makhluk sedang memerhatikannya. Salah seorang anak mereka, Lisa setiap malam akan turun ke sebuah bilik gelap untuk bermain congkak dengan seseorang yang hanya boleh dilihat olehnya seorang. Sufiah yang tidak boleh bersabar dengan perkara itu telah membuang congkak tersebut ke dalam tasik. Lisa juga sentiasa bermain di tepi belukar di belakang rumah kerana kawannya tinggal di situ sehingga Kazman perasan Lisa bermain menghadap kubur lama. Pada malam keesokannya, Sufiah dikejutkan lagi dengan bunyi congkak tersebut dari bilik yang sama. Apabila Sufiah pergi melihat, dilihatnya seorang tua sedang bemain congkak tersebut. Semakin lama peristiwa yang berlaku semakin pelik dan menyeramkan sehingga pada malam ketiga kedua-dua anaknya telah hilang dan Sufiah didapati tidur di siling bilik. Pak Tua, penduduk paling lama di kampung itu telah pergi ke rumah tersebut untuk menyelamatkan keluarga Kazman dan mencari Ely dan Lisa. Apakah sejarah sebenar banglo tersebut dan dapatkan Sufiah diselamatkan serta berjayakah Ely dan Lisa ditemui semula.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Pegawai penguatkuasa undang-undang Bunian 444 atau juga dikenali sebagai Black sedang diburu kerana rakan setugasnya seorang penderhaka, 419, telah melarikan diri ke dunia manusia. Menyedari 419 telah menghuni tubuh manusia, Black memutuskan untuk memasuki tubuh Malik untuk bersaing dengannya. Pada mata manusia, 'Malik' telah terselamat daripada kematian dengan menakjubkan sekali dan akibat kejadian itu dia telah hilang ingatan. Dalam pada itu, Sofia mula menyedari yang 'Malik' merupakan buat hatinya semasa kecil dan dia diselubungi rasa bersalah kerana telah meletak Malik dalam situasi bahaya. Namun 'Malik' sekarang ialah Black - biadab, mementingkan diri sendiri dan tekad dengan satu tujuan dalam misinya. Adakah dia akan ingat siapa Sofia sebenarnya? Black mendapati dirinya berdepan dengan pembunuhan yang mengerikan semasa dia cuba mengharungi dunia manusia. Keadaan menjadi lebih rumit apabila seorang lelaki yang penuh misteri muncul dan membayangi setiap gerak-gerinya.

programme.title: Azem 2
programme.desc: Beberapa orang membawa seorang gadis yang dirasuk teruk dengan kotak kayu berkunci untuk menyembuhkannya.

programme.title: The Invoking
programme.desc: Selepas mewarisi rumah daripada keluarga yang tidak pernah dikenalinya, Samantha Harris (Trin Miller) dan tiga rakannya menuju ke Sader Ridge luar bandar untuk memeriksa harta itu. Tidak lama selepas tiba, Sam mula mengalami penglihatan mengerikan tentang kekejaman ganas dan kejahatan yang tidak terkata. Diganggu oleh kuasa jahat yang mengepungnya, Sam mengalami mimpi ngeri apabila syaitan dari masa lalunya enggan terus dikebumikan lagi.

programme.title: Taxi 3
programme.desc: Sekumpulan pencuri yang menggelarkan diri mereka sebagai Geng Santa Claus sedang menimbulkan kekacauan, dan polis tidak dapat mengejarnya. Kapten polis Gilbert terganggu oleh seorang wartawan Cina yang menulis cerita tentang skuadnya, isteri detektif Emilien baru sahaja mengumumkan bahawa dia hamil, dan pemandu teksi Daniel sedang mengalami krisis hubungan. Selepas rentetan kesilapan di mana pencuri mengakali polis berkali-kali dengan wartawan di sana untuk merakam semuanya, Daniel dan teksi supernya masuk.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Seorang bapa yang ingin membalas dendam atas kematian isteri dan anaknya yang terbunuh mengikuti pembunuh, seorang pengutip hutang, kepada losmen pada suatu malam. Dengan pembunuh yang tinggal di bilik sebelah, kali ini hantu berlaku bukan dalam satu bilik tetapi dua. Dalam kejutan yang mengejutkan, di antara harta benda si mati, Golok menjumpai keratan akhbar lama yang menggambarkan sebuah keluarga yang hilang di motel berhantu itu, membayangkan bahawa bukan kebetulan mereka terjumpa Losmen Melati pada malam sebelumnya. Berapa ramai lagi yang tahu tentang rumah tamu terkutuk itu dan apakah masalah masa depan yang akan dibawa oleh ini?

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep 11 Ep11
programme.desc: Nina mendengar bacaan mantra datang dari bilik Echa. Apabila Nina menjenguk Echa terus histeria. Halim dan Nina membawa Echa pergi ke rumah Dawami setelah gagal dihubungi. Dipertengahan jalan, Echa merota dan melompar keluar dari kenderaan. Kebetulan Mat berada di tempat itu terus menyelamatkakn Echa dari dilanggar. Halim, Nina, Echa dan Mat pergi ke rumah Dawami untuk berubat Echa. Echa berjaya dipulih, sekaligus membuka dalang santau yang mengenai Nina. Mat dan Dawami mentarbiah Halim dan Nina supaya kembali ke jalan Allah.

programme.title: Langsuir
programme.desc: Azlan dan rakan-rakannya sedang bercuti, melawat pulau larangan Pulau Langsuir. Di sana, Azlan bertemu Suri, seorang gadis cantik, dan jatuh cinta kepadanya. Dia tidak tahu bahawa Suri adalah hantu 'langsuir' yang mendiami pulau itu. Iri hati dengan hubungan percintaan mereka, rakan-rakan Azlan merancang untuk menikam kepala Suri dengan paku untuk mendedahkan bentuk hantunya. Ini hanya membawa huru-hara kepada kumpulan itu kerana rancangan mereka telah menimbulkan kemarahan kakak Suri, Dewi.

programme.desc: Seorang isteri cemburu "zehra" meragui suaminya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan rakannya, dia merancang untuk melaksanakan sihir hitam oleh beberapa syeikh yang jahat untuk mendapatkan suaminya kembali daripada pesaingnya. Beberapa siri peristiwa hebat mula berlaku kepada rakannya berakhir dengan pembunuhan "zehra" y suaminya untuk mengelakkan skandal curang.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: The Lake
programme.desc: Seorang kanak-kanak membawa balik telur aneh, sehingga menyedari bahawa ia adalah telur raksasa. Ia muncul dari tasik dan membunuh semua orang di seluruh bandar.

programme.title: Den Budak Motor
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Deniel, seorang lelaki yang kecewa ditinggalkan oleh bekas kekasihnya, Sarah disebabkan kesusahan Deniel yang hanya memiliki motor kapcai.

programme.title: Superbike
programme.desc: Ia berkisar tentang kehidupan seharian sekumpulan penunggang motosikal superbike yang menggelar kumpulan mereka sebagai 'Pirate Bikers' dan diketuai oleh Bugs (Kamal Adli). Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Apabila salah seorang pemandu trak tunda muncul mati dan seorang lagi masih hilang, Detektif Fadil dari balai polis tempatan mula membuat hubungan antara kes terbarunya dan Losmen Melati. Dia mula bertanya soalan dan menghantar orang barunya, Osman, menyamar untuk mengetahui apa yang sebenarnya berlaku di losmen misteri itu. Tetapi apabila Osman hilang, Fadil bergegas ke losmen untuk mencarinya, hanya untuk melencong apabila dia melihat sesosok bayangan gelap di jalan raya di hadapannya, menyebabkan dia terbabas. Fadil sedar ada sesuatu yang lebih besar sedang bermain.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 5 Ep5
programme.desc: Melati mendedahkan niat sebenar dia yang ingin mengembalikan anaknya dari kematian. Dengan bantuan seorang Bomoh, Watih, Melati akan membawa pulang anaknya menggunakan darah yang dicuri daripada tetamu mudanya yang telah meninggal dunia sebelum ini. Namun, bukan anaknya sahaja yang ingin dibawa pulang. Melati telah membuat keputusan untuk membawa kembali Sigit - lelaki yang dibesarkannya, seorang lelaki yang mempunyai masa lalu yang kelam dan tragis - Melati percaya bahawa di sebalik kengerian masa lalunya, dia layak mendapat peluang kedua. Makhluk jahat yang pernah terperangkap di ruang bawah tanah didedahkan di Kusno, makhluk jahat dan jahat serta bapa Sigit. Apabila Kusno mula membunuh, dia mula menjadi lebih kuat dan mula menyerupai bentuk manusianya sekali lagi. Kusno mempunyai satu misi untuk memusnahkan Melati. Tetapi Kusno tidak bersendirian. Dengan menggunakan kuasanya yang semakin meningkat, dia memihak kepada bentuk jahat lelaki yang membunuh ibu Melati pada tahun 1900-an - Pemburu.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 6 Ep6
programme.desc: Selepas lebih satu abad, Melati akhirnya bertemu semula dengan anaknya, Ari. Ari mula mengingati masa lalunya dan bagaimana dia mati. Melati mendedahkan kebenaran Sigit dan Kusno. Walaupun Melati berharap peluang kedua akan menjadikan dia lelaki yang lebih baik, Watih masih tidak mempercayai Sigit. Dia memberi amaran kepadanya bahawa jika dia bertindak menentang Melati dan keluarganya, dia mempunyai kuasa untuk merobek jiwanya dari tubuh barunya. Sara, seorang detektif polis dari bandar dan rakan keluarga Fadil bimbang tentang dia selepas radionya senyap dan memutuskan untuk menjelajah ke negara itu untuk memastikan dia baik-baik saja. Dengan semua tanda menunjuk kepada Losmen Melati, Sara menuju ke rumah terkutuk itu. Semasa Watih berlepas dari Losmen Melati, dia diserang oleh Kusno. Dia membunuh Watih, membalas dendam pertamanya.

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Melati, Golok, Sigit dan Ari bersiap sedia untuk melawan Kusno. Sara memasuki losmen mencari Fadil tetapi akhirnya terperangkap di salah satu bilik. Di sana, dia mendapati Fadil terperangkap dalam perigi dari episod 4. Diserang oleh roh rumah, Sara cuba menyelamatkan Fadil dan akhirnya mengorbankan dirinya dalam proses itu. Melati meyakinkan arwah rumah untuk berpihak kepadanya dalam perjuangannya menentang Kusno. Kusno dan Pemburu menyerang Losmen Melati. Sigit berbaik semula dengan Ari atas kengerian masa lalunya dan menentang ayahnya untuk kebaikan. Kini keluar dari perigi, Fadil cuba keluar dari rumah tetapi tersedut untuk melawan Kusno. Berjuang melawan Kusno sendiri, Fadil berada di ambang kematian apabila Kusno menggigitnya, membiarkan kutukan memasuki sistemnya. Apabila semua kelihatan hilang untuk Melati, dia mendedahkan senjata rahsianya - Watih, yang Kusno dipercayai telah mati, kembali untuk memberikan pukulan maut terakhir, akhirnya mengalahkan Kusno sekali dan untuk selama-lamanya. Namun apabila hari baru menjelma, Fadil muncul semula, tetapi semuanya tidak seperti yang disangka. Mata Fadil menjadi hitam, membayangkan kisah Losmen Melati belum berakhir.

programme.title: You Saka… Pergi Jauh-jauh Ep 4 Ep4
programme.desc: Nia yang baru bangun pagi kelihatan gelisah akibat mimpi tuan puteri ingin memberikannya sekuntum bunga dan dia menceritakan kepada Shasa. Shasa hanya menyatakan kerana Nia terbawa-bawa dan memikirkan yang dia alami. Sementara itu, Pak Abas dan Roslan bercakap tentang arwah Rosserita. Di pejabat, Nia diganggui oleh saka Gelam. Manakala di rumah dia terserempak depan berdepan dengan lembaga putih berdialog dan memberi amaran kepadanya. Kemudiannnya menceritakan pengalamannya bahawa lembaga putih itu menyerupai emaknya. Manakala Fauzan dengan ibunya bertengkar kerana ibunya bercadang untuk menghantar ke hospital gila. Ini berikutan Fauzan bercakap dengan seseorang kononnya berada di atas bangku disebelahnya.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: Seorang pesara tentera Cina British, seorang lelaki muda Asia Selatan, pertemuan di Chungking Mansions. Kebetulan mereka berdua menyinggung perasaan bos geng yang sama. Apa yang telah memberi mereka nafas baru dan bagaimana mereka menemui semula diri mereka melalui syarikat masing-masing.

programme.title: Nayang
programme.desc: Seorang penulis skrip bernama Eysha sedang mencari bahan untuk menulis kisah misteri yang berlaku di sebuah kampung terpencil bernama Kampung Nayang. Di sana dia bertemu Nek Som yang tahu akan kisah itu. Menurut cerita Nek Som, di kampung itu dahulu tinggal seorang wanita bernama Nayang yang sering diganggu Jalak dan rakan-rakannya ketika suaminya dipenjara akibat difitnah. Ketika itulah berlaku satu tragedi sehingga mengakibatkan kekecohan di seluruh kampung itu.

programme.title: Aku Bukan Pendatang
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Sudin yang mendapat tugasan untuk menghantar kereta pejabatnya ke Singapura. Dalam perjalanannya menuju Kota Singa, Sudin bertemu dengan Zaharah dan Mayon di sebuah kawasan rehat dan menumpangkan mereka berdua ke Johor Bahru. Tanpa disedari, Sudin telah kehilangan pasportnya dan dia terperangkap dalam satu sindiket pemalsuan dokumen. Pelbagai kejadian berlaku sehingga Sudin dianggap sebagai pendatang asing tanpa izin.

programme.title: Rahsia
programme.desc: Dihantui gangguan misteri, sepasang suami isteri mula mencari punca kepada gangguan tersebut. Profesor Hamdan dan Ramlah serta anak mereka, Saiful dan Marina berpindah ke sebuah banglo lama di tepi laut. Mereka hidup aman dan damai bersama di banglo tersebut. Namun tragedi melanda apabila Marina lemas di laut dan meninggal dunia - dari situlah bermulanya kejadian aneh.

programme.title: Bapak Borek Anak Rintik
programme.desc: Johan merupakan seorang pemuda yang memiliki kelebihan semulajadi dari segi kepantasan dan tenaga. Johan bertekad untuk mencari ayahnya yang tidak pernah ditemuinya sejak dilahirkan. Dalam pencarian itu Johan telah menyelamatkan Osman yang sedang ditimpa masalah. Johan yakin Osman ialah ayahnya yang dicari cari selama ini. Perkenalan dengan Osman telah melibatkan Johan dalam masalah yang lebih besar. Johan yang lurus bendul itu telah dipergunakan Osman untuk melakukan tugas-tugas mengintip Julia, gadis pisau cukur. Keadaan menjadi lebih huru-hara apabila Johan berkenalan dan dengan Fiza.

programme.title: Suratan Kasih
programme.desc: Sunny mengalami tekanan jiwa selepas melihat ibunya yang sedang berzina mati dibunuh ayahnya sendiri. Apabila meningkat dewasa, Sunny menjadi seorang pembunuh bersiri di sebalik kerjayanya sebagai komposer dan pemuzik. Mangsanya ialah golongan perempuan yang melakukan perbuatan zina. Dalam masa yang sama, Sunny mencintai seorang penyanyi baharu yang bernama Natasha.

programme.title: Alahai Kekasihku
programme.desc: Rini seorang wanita berbadan besar yang ingin mengurangkan berat badannya. Namun dia sering gagal untuk berbuat sedemikian kerana dia suka makan. Di pejabat, Rini sering bertikam lidah dengan Norman yang selalu menyakitkan hatinya. Dalam masa yang sama, Rini jatuh cinta dengan seorang lelaki yang dikenalinya di internet. Apabila mereka bercadang untuk berjumpa buat kali pertama, Rini berusaha dengan lebih giat untuk menjadi kurus.

programme.title: Misteri Rumah Tua
programme.desc: Dendam lama mula terbalas apabila hadirnya sekumpulan remaja ke sebuah rumah lama yang dihuni roh wanita. Sebuah pembunuhan kejam telah berlaku di rumah tersebut apabila dia dirogol dan dibunuh ketika sedang sarat mengandung. Wanita tersebut ingin membalas dendam kerana ketidakadilan yang telah berlaku ketika dirinya masih hidup. Bapa kepada salah seorang dari kumpulan remaja tersebut pula pernah terlibat dengan pembunuhan kejam wanita itu yang menaikkan lagi rasa marah roh tersebut. Pelbagai insiden menyeramkan mula terjadi di rumah itu.

programme.title: Dendam Pelamin

programme.title: Jengka

programme.title: Nayang
programme.desc: Seorang penulis skrip bernama Eysha sedang mencari bahan untuk menulis kisah misteri yang berlaku di sebuah kampung terpencil bernama Kampung Nayang. Di sana dia bertemu Nek Som yang tahu akan kisah itu. Menurut cerita Nek Som, di kampung itu dahulu tinggal seorang wanita bernama Nayang yang sering diganggu Jalak dan rakan-rakannya ketika suaminya dipenjara akibat difitnah. Ketika itulah berlaku satu tragedi sehingga mengakibatkan kekecohan di seluruh kampung itu.

programme.title: Bapak Borek Anak Rintik
programme.desc: Johan merupakan seorang pemuda yang memiliki kelebihan semulajadi dari segi kepantasan dan tenaga. Johan bertekad untuk mencari ayahnya yang tidak pernah ditemuinya sejak dilahirkan. Dalam pencarian itu Johan telah menyelamatkan Osman yang sedang ditimpa masalah. Johan yakin Osman ialah ayahnya yang dicari cari selama ini. Perkenalan dengan Osman telah melibatkan Johan dalam masalah yang lebih besar. Johan yang lurus bendul itu telah dipergunakan Osman untuk melakukan tugas-tugas mengintip Julia, gadis pisau cukur. Keadaan menjadi lebih huru-hara apabila Johan berkenalan dan dengan Fiza.

programme.desc: In a bad economy, many people dream of becoming rich overnight, especially the Jiang family. Mother Jiang pushes her three children to earn money so that they can one day live in luxury. Even her daughter-in-law wishes for the same thing. She hopes that one day she can visit her parents with the money that spills out of her purse.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: July Rhapsody
programme.desc: A 40-year-old high school teacher is in midlife crisis, his marriage is on the rocks and he is involved in a taboo romance with a female student who has a crush on him. Meanwhile, his wife is off to care for her dying ex-lover who shares a complicated history with the couple...

programme.title: I Believe
programme.desc: Chu Chu has been waiting for her first love for 10 years but he marries someone else in the end. As she loses faith in love, she meets a wedding planner and a handsome and rich man, who both help her get over her ex-boyfriend. As Chu Chu feels the same love from them, she must make up her mind. Who will she choose in the end?

programme.title: P Storm
programme.desc: Ping reports a case of a rich mans son bribing prison guards to cover up his criminal activities in the prison to the ICAC. ICAC officer Luk goes undercover in prison to conduct his investigation. Despite the risks involved, Luk is determined to complete his mission with the help of his cell mate, Wang.

programme.title: Find Your Voice
programme.desc: The passion choir pilot program trains students from three underperforming schools choir to participate in an inter-school choral competition. While it seems impossible, a renowned conductor, Yim Tsz Long, unexpectedly agrees to lead the choir. Will the passion choir and Maestro Yim complete this impossible mission and win the competition?

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Crypto Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigation officer Lok sets up a special team to investigate a corruption case involving a banks top executives use of cryptocurrency to manipulate the trading market. When the banks chairman is kidnapped and kidnappers demand ransom in crypto coins, Lok connects the dots and vows to hunt down the mastermind behind both crimes.

programme.title: Tales from the Occult: Body and Soul
programme.desc: This horror anthology series returns to feature three spooky crime stories about an ex-hair model, a cat lover and the love triangle between a dental nurse, a dentist and a chef. The stories depict their paths from obsession to madness, eventually tipping them over to the dark side of human nature.

programme.title: Song of Spring
programme.desc: An 85-year-old mother lives with her 65-year-old daughter who is suffering from Alzheimer's disease, causing her to suffer a decline in memory, mental confusion and disorientation. Though the elderly mother has to shoulder the burden of a caregiver, she still wants to be with her daughter forever.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: Confinement
programme.desc: Si Ling, a pregnant painter, moves into her dream home after winning an award and hires a confinement nanny. As she begins her one-month confinement after giving birth to her daughter, inexplicable incidents start happening in the house, threatening both her and her baby

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Player
programme.desc: Chinese Feng Shui master, Carson (Chapman To) was a "Natural Born Player", taking names and breaking hearts. Fate had it that he would meet his match, the hot veterinarian, Chi-Ling (Chrissie Chau). It was love at first sight but neither could stand the other's fickle nature lest the affair might have ended as soon as it began.

programme.title: Bullet and Brain
programme.desc: Nine years ago, two legendary criminals, Bullet and Brain, vowed not to kill and lie before they disappeared. Both now return for a mission - to protect the granddaughter of the triad boss. Can they succeed without breaking their vows?

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: Fight Back to School
programme.desc: The number one killer in SDU, Chow Sing Sing(Stephen Chow), is sent to a school to find a lost gun. His partner Tat(Ng Man Tat) pretends to be a school worker in assisting him. They recognize that some students are being closed with Fei, the head of triad society, and Fei traffics munitions. Sing steals and ignites Fei's munitions; Fei pledges to kill Sing...

programme.title: The Lost Bladesman
programme.desc: An epic historic adventure set during the turbulent times of the Three Kingdoms. Cao Cao attempts to enlist Guan Yu into his forces, but Guan is loyal to his sworn brother Liu Bei, who is also Caos enemy. As Guan tries to rescue Liu Beis concubine from Cao, he is forced to fight his way through. Can he succeed in the end?

programme.title: Ready O/R Rot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi are finally getting married but pressure from Guys mother creates much friction between them. Meanwhile, Grey Bear suspects his wife of cheating on him and Ken faces the biggest crisis of his life when Jessica accidentally gets pregnant. Can they eventually solve their relationship problems?

programme.title: Song of the Assassins
programme.desc: A young assassin is assigned his first mission while secretly investigating the cause of his familys massacre years ago. While taking on the mission, he finds himself entangled in a political conspiracy that was planned for years and has to use his skills as an assassin to solve whatever comes his way.

programme.title: Inner Senses
programme.desc: Haunted by recurring visions stemming from past traumas, Yan reaches out to psychiatrist Dr Jim to restore her sanity and overcome her troubled past. Yet, as Yan gradually heals, Jim finds himself haunted by the same disturbing images, as his suppressed memories resurface.

programme.title: Echoes of the Thunder
programme.desc: Two half-brothers, Nam and Fire, are top racing drivers. In a racing challenge with Japanese driver Kenji, Nam causes a young racing driver to be seriously injured and is depressed. Fire stands up for Nam and decides to compete with Kenji in an illegal street car race. Who will win the race? Can Nam finally bounce back?

programme.title: City Under Siege
programme.desc: When circus clown Sunny gets transformed into a super-powered mutant, he finds himself pitted against his fellow circus performers who were altered in the same accident, and who are now using their powers to wreak havoc around the city.

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: Midnight Diner
programme.desc: A small restaurant in Shanghai is open only from midnight to early morning. The chef has no menu but will create something unique for each customer. Through the years, people come to the Midnight Diner to share their stories, taste the chefs delicious food and leave feeling comforted and fulfilled.

programme.title: Beauty And The 7 Beasts
programme.desc: Teddy, once a renowned movie star, is facing a career decline. To make a living, he accepts five disciples to shape them into stars. Teddys career regains momentum after he reunites with his long-lost daughter, but he is also confronted by a rival at the same time. His daughter and disciples decide to help him overcome this difficult situation

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: The Gangster, the Cop, the Devil
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from real events. Detective Lin sets up a special unit to arrest the motorbike robber and the crime syndicate behind the thefts in Foshan. In the process, his pregnant wife is hit by a motorbike robber, leading him to uncover their revenge plan...

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: Death Notice
programme.desc: A serial killer leaves death notices in a city, stating when, how and who he will murder. Even if the victims report it to the police and receive protection, the killer can still break through and execute them. While the police sets up a special task force in response, they expose an even bigger conspiracy behind.

programme.title: Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: A group of bounty hunters, including San, Yo, Cat, Swan and Bobo, are tasked to track down the culprit of a series of bombings that have plagued an international hotel group. Unfortunately, Swan, Cat and Bobo are kidnapped by the mastermind of the bombings. Can San and Yo save them? Will the bounty hunters accomplish their mission?

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Chois actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: Better Days
programme.desc: In this Oscar nominee for Best International Feature Film, Nian faces relentless bullying from her peers as she prepares for her college entrance exam. Fate leads her to streetwise punk Bei, but before they can retreat into their own world, both are embroiled in a murder investigation that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: The Master
programme.desc: Gao Jian is the disciple of the martial arts master Shi but is constantly being punished by his master for no reason. One day, Gao accidentally saves his masters rival Jin, so Jin teaches him his unique martial arts skill in return. However, Master Shi sees this as Gaos betrayal

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung And The Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung meets a famous courtesan in Suzhou and in order to spend as much time as possible with her, he builds a direct underground tunnel into the Forbidden City. The emperors sudden appearances through this direct access shock his people but it is also at this time that he helps the needy and cracks the gambling business in Suzhou.

programme.title: Oath Of Death
programme.desc: Three Sung loyalists become blood brothers to fight the tyranny of the Tartar invaders. To oust the oppressors altogether, Ma releases the kidnapped Tartar princess in a strategic effort to gain points with the invaders, but it soon becomes apparent that he desires both a great position and power, and will do anything to get it

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent. The girl brings happiness to the Xus until her long lost mother appears one day and to make her happy, Mrs Xu reluctantly lets the girl reunite with her mother.

programme.title: Heroes Of Sung
programme.desc: Heroes Of Sung stars one of the original kung fu ladies of the silver screen, Shih Szu, who plays swordswoman Meng Hung. She must work with Fan Tien-Fu, played by Lo Lieh to find and protect the royal seals of the Sung Dynasty. Shih's magnificent performance earned her the female hero role in another hit Dracula And The 7 Golden Vampires.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: The Thundering Sword
programme.desc: Two disciples, Yu and Zheng, are sent by their master to track down the invincible weapon Thundering Sword to prevent villains from getting it. Yu encounters the daughter of a ruthless clan, Chiao, who is on her way to seek for the sword. They quickly fall for each other, but when Chiao accidentally injures Zheng, things become complicated.

programme.title: Mr. Funnybone Strikes Again
programme.desc: In this hilarious sequel, Mr Big Potato opens an old-fashioned Chinese clinic, but his traditional methods are rejected by the sceptics of modern Hong Kong. Enter his buddy Mr Funny bone to rescue his business!

programme.title: Ghosts Galore
programme.desc: Young Taoist priest Lu and his friend are nearly killed by a female ghost during an exorcism. Luckily, Master Lian saves their lives, so they beseech him to teach them his skills. When his friend is killed by ruthless ninjas, Lu decides to learn the ultimate witchcraft and teams up with his master to defeat them.

programme.title: Woman Of The Night
programme.desc: The movie offers three stories of love and obsession. In the first tale, a young student with a voyeuristic habit spies on two of his female roommates. The second story follows an office manager who develops an infatuation for his secretary. The last story is a complex family drama about a debilitated father who forces his family to leave him.

programme.title: Dead End
programme.desc: Uninhibited youth Chun meets a rich girl Wen when her car breaks down and drives her home. Chun falls in love with Wen but Wens brother dislikes him and forbids his sister to see him. He humiliates Chun and gets Chun beaten up, so Chun takes the pistol he has found accidentally on the street to Wens home and shoots her brother dead.

programme.title: The House Of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: The Twin Bracelets
programme.desc: Two teenage girls make a pledge to look after each other in a small Chinese fishing town, where the notions of women's rights or sexual freedom are absent. One ends up happily married to a stranger, while the other is cruelly betrothed to the abusive son of a wealthy family and has to seek to free herself from the situation.

programme.title: Pursuit Of Vengeance
programme.desc: Kung Fu legend Ti Lung stars in the action movie as Fu Xue Hong, embarking on a epic journey of revenge for his father.

programme.title: The Singing Escort
programme.desc: Betty Ting plays Susan, a young woman hiding from her father by being a nightclub singer in Japan. Pop singer Chao Ke-jen (Lin Chong) gets permission from his boss to visit Japan, with the condition that he finds the boss's daughter. Boy finds girl, boy falls in love. But will the father approve?

programme.title: That Man In Chang-An
programme.desc: The Han Emperor dies and his Empress Lu seizes the ruling power. She plots to kill the heir to the throne, Liu Heng, but the masked warrior discovers her plot and tips off Liu. Liu sends his princess to Chang An to ask for help. The masked warrior protects the princess from attackers along the way and supports Liu to become the new Emperor.

programme.title: The Amorous Lotus Pan
programme.desc: Adapted from the renowned Chinese novel, The Water Margin, this is the story of a poor and beautiful girl Lotus Pan, who is raped by her master and had to be married off to a midget who treats her badly. Lost and lonely, Pan unwittingly becomes a pawn in the game of lust between her husbands playboy brother Wu Song, and a murderous man Men Ching.

programme.title: Godfather Of Canton
programme.desc: A docker, Lin Si Hai, accidentally saves Commissioner Cheng who then offers him a position in the police force. Lin is smart and soon rises through the ranks through treachery and corruption, before becoming a gangster.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Sam is being hunted as he discovers that the mayor and the chief of medical bureau are colluding with a drug dealer. He is saved by a fishermen family and works in their friends grocery but the grocery owner is killed when the enemies track Sam down. Sam escapes to Shaolin to learn the cudgel style of kung fu in order to avenge his friends.

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: Secret Service Of The Imperial Court
programme.desc: Zhao Bu Fan is the sergeant of the governments secret police. Wang is a cruel and ruthless eunuch who takes over the Emperors ruling power and leads the team of secret agents. After witnessing the atrocities committed by Eunuch Wang, Sergeant Zhao decides to defect but ends up being hunted by his friends, comrades and even his father.

programme.title: Return Of The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: Killer Constable
programme.desc: Kuei Chih-hung was famous for his modern day crime thrillers, his horror flicks, and even his comedies. But if the only kung-fu film he ever made was this one, hed still be spoken of with respect by even the most ardent martial arts movie fan. Many consider this real life martial arts champion Chen Kuan-tais best performance. As a deeply, even obsessively, dedicated Chief Court Constable, he illuminates the screen with fighting skill and emotional passion. Award winning actor Ku Feng is his equal, playing an especially homicidal robber-chief who thinks nothing of throwing all his men at their relentless pursuer. Lu Tsun and Huang Pei-chi choreograph the many battles featuring such action stalwarts as Pai Piao and Ai Fei.

programme.title: Crazy Shaolin Disciples
programme.desc: Three young kung-fu warriors from wildly different backgrounds become students of Shaolin at the same temple. These three warriors are: Royal Guard Lo Lieh, fleeing soldier, Lo Meng, and villager, Wang Yu.

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical comedy is about how a young man Fen, along with his buddy Hamburger, finds love and success in the advertising world.

programme.title: Brave Archer And His Mate
programme.desc: Guo Jing and Huang Rong raise the son of his sworn brother Yang Kang and named him Yang Guo. To prevent Yang Guo from taking revenge for his fathers death, Huang Rong bans him from learning martial arts. Yang Guo runs away from home in anger and encounters Ouyang Feng, who teaches him the Toad Stance and accidentally unveils his true identity

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Wits Of The Brats
programme.desc: Tou Kuan is a wealthy Kwangtung brat with a good kung fu background, he has only one ambition: to pit his wits against three shady masters of the North. The first, conman Che Tsai. The second, a professional romantic dubbed The Terrific. Terrific introduces Tou Kuan to his third rival, Thief Shih San-shou.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends help.

programme.title: The Naval Commandos
programme.desc: The Chinese Navy is attempting to defend its coastline from a Japanese attack, they send their commando unit led by Cui Hsia into the mainland to enlist help to thwart the Japanese before they attack. The commandos enlist the help of Song San and Shiao Liu to kill the Japanese officers led by Shan Mao and destroy their attacking ships.

programme.title: Songfest
programme.desc: As its name implies, Songfest is an Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musical, traditionally Chinese and timeless in content; yet revealing a spirited and modern technique. Shot on location at Taiwan's beautiful Sun-Moon Lake, it's a turbulent romance between a passionate tea picker Sung Yu Lan and a charming fisherman Li Chun Yang.

programme.title: The Fighting Fool
programme.desc: Famous Kung Fu Pole master Red Eagle, is kidnapped by a villain one day. His disciple Meng, vows to rescue him. On his way, Meng encounters a greedy but great martial artist who agrees to join him in the rescue. Even though the two have extremely different personalities, they manage to team up and fight the villain in a final showdown.

programme.title: Mist Over Dream Lake
programme.desc: A young girl Chen is sent away by her parents who are going through divorce, to stay with the Changs. On the Changs farm, she meets their two sons, the youngest daughter and a young artist, and spends a summer with them that she will never forget.

programme.title: Dirty Ho
programme.desc: Master Wang, who is actually the 11th prince, poses as an antique connoisseur to hide his true identity. When he meets Dirty Ho, a witty con artist, Wang knows he has found the right man to help him untangle a royal succession plot...

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep2
programme.desc: Pop Night - After Maceos dad, Albert, injured himself in the premiere episode, host Philip Lawrence declared all 12 teams safe from elimination, making this weeks Pop Night the first emotional goodbye of the season.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep3
programme.desc: Bust A Groove Night, Part 1 - The stakes are at an all-time high when each kid is tasked with teaching their parent three dance moves that they must incorporate into their performance.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep4
programme.desc: Bust A Groove Night, Part 2 - The second wave of five kids tasks their dance partners with learning three new moves that they must pull off during their performances. The five remaining teams perform dance routines on part two of a two-part episode.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep5
programme.desc: Picture This - Emotions are at an all-time high as each team performs a routine inspired by a photo that represents their relationship.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep6
programme.desc: #Throwback - Each of the final eight teams chooses their favorite era to inspire the creation of an original performance. From ancient Egypt through present day, teams are pushed out of their comfort zones as they perform routines to songs.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep7
programme.desc: Musical Magic - Drawing inspiration from their favorite musicals, each dance team is faced with the daunting task of showcasing their theatrical skills. Seven parent-kid teams remain in the competition as they perform dance routines to hit musical songs.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep8
programme.desc: Jet Setters - Six teams perform dances inspired by their dream destinations, and one team makes history when they receive the first-ever perfect score in the competition.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep9
programme.desc: Heroes Night - Each team is tasked with creating their own superhero power as they battle their way through difficult dance routines, in hopes of advancing to the semi-final. The talented kids and their untrained parents perform routines to hits.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep10
programme.desc: Semi-Final - The four remaining teams dance not once, but twice to prove they have what it takes to advance to the grand finale. The final four perform routines to top songs.

programme.title: Come Dance With Me Ep11
programme.desc: Grand Finale - The judges and choreographers kick off the shows season finale with an epic dance, then the three final kid-parent teams perform encores of the judges favorite routines from the season with the winning duo taking home the $100,000 grand prize!

programme.title: Extreme Africa 1 - Dragon Mountain: Surviving the Summit Ep1
programme.desc: South Africa's Drakensberg is one of the continent's most impressive landscapes. It is home to sharp climatic and ecological gradients as physical conditions change for both land-based creatures and the Raptors that swirl in the skies above.

programme.title: Extreme Africa 1 - Lake Manyara National Park Ep2
programme.desc: In north Tanzania, towering mountains line a dramatic valley. Enriched by ancient volcanoes, its slopes provide a variety of habitats for life to thrive and its great centerpiece holds water through even the driest of times.

programme.title: Extreme Africa 1 - The Simien Mountains Ep3
programme.desc: Simien Mountains National Park in Ethiopia is home to some of the rarest creatures on earth. Take a glimpse into life on some of the highest peaks in Africa, in the last stronghold of shaggy, grass-grazing Geladas, elusive Simien wolves and horned Walia ibex.

programme.title: Extreme Africa 1 - The Southern Drylands Ep4
programme.desc: The Southern Drylands is a journey into the most arid and extreme environments in the furthest reaches of southern Africa. We go to spectacular but treacherous places where almost no rain falls, to find incredibly resilient creatures and learn the secrets to their survival. From the largest mammals to the fastest insects and even a ghost-like fish found nowhere else in the world, the Southern Drylands contain some extraordinary inhabitants, all connected by the daily challenges of living in some of most inhospitable habitats in the world.

programme.title: Extreme Africa 1 - Etosha: The Great White Place Ep5
programme.desc: Etosha was once a great lake that dried up and now only fills with water seasonally during the summer rains. Once the Etosha pan is full of water, a myriad of water birds congregate in the shallow lake to breed, most notably Greater and lesser flamingos.

programme.title: Extreme Africa 1 - The Linear Oasis Ep6
programme.desc: Follow the course of South Africas Orange river from its origins to where it spills out into the Atlantic Ocean. Along the way we encounter a diverse range of habitats and the creatures they support, from the dry lands of the Richtersveld to the beauty of Augrabies; this is the story of the Linear Oasis. We reveal how life is adapted to survive along its course and discover a rich world of plants and animals.

programme.title: Africa's Hunters 1 - The Hungry Leopard Ep1
programme.desc: A revolutionary thermal camera reveals the secret world of nocturnal predators. Follow along as one of the oldest-known leopards struggles to survive her fearsome neighbors: a pride of scavenging lions.

programme.title: Shadowlands 1 - Bound By Blood Ep1
programme.desc: Experience unbelievable acts of courage and loyalty by creatures trying to survive in the remote wilderness of New Zealands South Island. Face forest penguins feast and famine cycles, and explore the tumultuous world of newborn sea lions.

programme.title: Shadowlands 1 - Life in Dark Water Ep2
programme.desc: Learn how winters arrival triggers animal survival instincts in southwestern New Zealand. Track dolphins as they move to warmer waters to give their calves a fighting chance, and join longfin eels on an epic migration to their spawning grounds.

programme.title: Shadowlands 1 - Age of Independence Ep3
programme.desc: The south-eastern coast of New Zealand are some of the richest fishing grounds in the world the place for young marine animals to transition from novices to independent adults. Young whales, dolphins and seals learn to hunt, learn the rules of society, or strike out on their own adventures.

programme.title: America's Wild Border: Northern Exposure
programme.desc: Trail Atlantic puffins, Prairie rattlesnakes, Alaskan caribou and other animals as they travel across the international boundary between the U.S. and Canada. See how they can move from safety to target by crossing a line they had no say in creating.

programme.title: Animals Decoded 1 - Body Language Ep1
programme.desc: Join researchers as they study how animals communicate. Find out how wolves use their body language to unite the pack and maintain a sophisticated social structure, and see the astounding number of gestures chimps use to communicate.

programme.title: Carpathian Predators 1 - Realm of the Bear Ep1
programme.desc: Join a mother brown bear as she struggles to find food for her two young cubs while teaching them essential skills for the harsh winter ahead. Then visit a pair of tiny lynx kittens as they begin to venture away from the safety of their den.

programme.title: Carpathian Predators 1 - Realm of the Wolf Ep2
programme.desc: In the remote wilderness of the Carpathian Mountains lives an elusive predator that has inspired awe and fear throughout history: the Eurasian wolf. Discover the vital role that these once-misunderstood hunters play in protecting their ecosystem.

programme.title: The Hungry Games: Alaska's Big Bear Challenge 1 - Welcome to the Tundra Ep1
programme.desc: Wake up post-hibernation with 7 ravenous bears as Stage 1 of the competition kicks off. Battle wolves with new mom BoldFace, see tiny Stomper vie for power and Blondies love, and stand back as grizzled vet Bernie brawls with clueless teen Casanova.

programme.title: Gladiators 1 - Waterhole Ep1
programme.desc: Witness clashes over precious resources when the dry season brings a band of gladiators to an African savannah watering hole. See a lion-elephant territory brawl, an ant raid on a termite mound, and a honey badgers risky dance with a deadly snake.

programme.title: Gladiators 1 - Wild Coast Ep2
programme.desc: Go up against Australias wiliest gladiators and their impressive arsenals. Learn if these weapons, such as the kangaroos deadly boxing moves and the redback spiders precision-engineered traps, can help them survive the ravages of climate change.

programme.title: How the Wild Things Sleep
programme.desc: Tap into one of the least understood areas of animal science: sleep. Check out adaptations made by the most extreme snoozers on Earth, from tiny bees who doze for 20 hours a day to enormous elephants who survive on just two precious hours of rest.

programme.title: Extreme Africa 1 - Dragon Mountain: Surviving the Summit Ep1
programme.desc: South Africa's Drakensberg is one of the continent's most impressive landscapes. It is home to sharp climatic and ecological gradients as physical conditions change for both land-based creatures and the Raptors that swirl in the skies above.

programme.title: Extreme Africa 1 - Lake Manyara National Park Ep2
programme.desc: In north Tanzania, towering mountains line a dramatic valley. Enriched by ancient volcanoes, its slopes provide a variety of habitats for life to thrive and its great centerpiece holds water through even the driest of times.

programme.title: Mysteries of Evolution 1 - Ancient Lineages Ep6
programme.desc: Some call them living fossils, but that's just another way to say survivors. From the shark to the horseshoe crab, these animals' early adaptations were a success, leaving them relatively unchanged for millions of years.

programme.title: Waterworld Africa 1 - Wetland Wonder Ep8
programme.desc: South Africas greatest wetland, Lake St. Lucia, provides sustenance for animals that depend on standing water, including hippos, crocs, and countless water birds. But during a drought, the system faces challenges that have devastating consequences.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - The Borderlands Ep1
programme.desc: Where the mountains cross international borders, herds of elk and moose live side by side with predators like bears and wolves. The predator/prey relationship is a delicate balance, and the perfect place to see it in action is the Kootenay area of the Rocky Mountains.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - In the Peaks Ep2
programme.desc: The air is thin and cold, trees cant even live here - its not exactly a welcoming place to live. But animals like mountain goats and bighorn sheep and even black bears manage to skitter around these peaks with ease. Well take a look at how these creatures manage to defy gravity, among some of the highest peaks on the continent.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - The Waterways Ep3
programme.desc: Some of mightiest rivers in North America originate on the glacial heights of the Rocky Mountains. The lakes, rivers and marshes of the Rockies are like arteries pulsing through the landscape, feeding the creatures that call the mountains home. Fed by glaciers and motivated by gravity, these waterways are split by the massive Rockies, which divert flow into the Atlantic, Pacific, and Arctic Oceans. From the uninhabitable icy pecks, water melts off glaciers, runs down thunderous waterfalls, filters through wetlands, sculpts the terrain, and finally flows out to the ocean, sustaining life and transforming environments along the way.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - Balancing the Forest Ep4
programme.desc: Survival in the forest means maintaining a delicate balance between growth and destruction and death and rebirth - a forest should be in a constant state of regeneration. When trees get too tall they block all the sunlight from hitting the ground, which means grasses and smaller shrubs cant grow, diminishing habitat for animals like elk, moose, caribou, and wolves.

programme.title: Wild Rockies 1 - Group Survival Ep5
programme.desc: For a great many species, the structures of group living are the most important for survival. Although social living is integral to many of the animals that call the Rocky Mountains home, no two species organize their society in the same way. Even among closely related species there can be drastic differences in social structure; communication, hierarchy, mating, and diet are all inextricably informed by specific environmental and genetic adaptations for group survival.

programme.title: Africa's Hidden Kingdoms 1 - The Drakensberg: Barrier of Spears Ep1
programme.desc: This documentary looks at the wildlife of The Drakensberg Mountain range. We take a look at how creatures survive in the hostile landscape, from the highest peaks to the rolling grasslands below.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 - July-August - a Time of Migration Ep4
programme.desc: Witness some of the planets most dramatic natural shifts in July, from the Arctic ice sheets that come crashing down during the summer melt to the feeding frenzy when sockeye salmon reach the end of their journey in Alaska.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 - September-October - a Time of Activation Ep5
programme.desc: Travel around the world to see another seasonal change unfold. The Northern Hemisphere moves into autumn, while Australia witnesses a rebirth of life, and mating humpbacks fill the warming tropical seas of Tonga.

programme.title: A Wild Year on Earth 1 - November-December - Full Circle Ep6
programme.desc: Witness some of the most incredible natural events in November, from the millions of Monarch butterflies that converge in Mexicos forests to the deep fog that shrouds the city of Dubai, signalling the start of winter.

programme.title: Colombia's Wild Coast 1 - Snake Prison Island Ep1
programme.desc: Gorgona was once home to Colombias Alcatraz. Modelled on Nazi concentration camps, prisoners dreamt of escape. See the islands stunning wildlife through the eyes of a convict on the run, the monkeys, snakes and sloths whove now reclaimed the land.

programme.title: Colombia's Wild Coast 1 - March of the Crabs Ep2
programme.desc: On the island of Providencia, a black crab begins the mission of her life, escorting 80,000 eggs from her home, on a 3 km hike to the coast. Join her, and millions of her clan, on a journey fraught with danger, where chances of survival are slim.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway 1 - Into the Darkness Ep3
programme.desc: Stay up late as the northern team attaches an activity tag to a bull shark and finds out what this night owl does after sunset. Then dive 80 meters deep with the southern team, who are hoping to put a satellite tracker on a female great white.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway 1 - The Social Network Ep4
programme.desc: Ponder shark community hierarchies as the northern team studies how young blacktips learn social and survival skills. Then rush to Rainbow Beach with the southern team, who are eager to witness the sand tiger sharks most elusive behaviour: mating.

programme.title: Super Shark Highway 1 - Detour Ep5
programme.desc: Travel to the ends of Australias shark highways. Find out if Greenly Island in the south is a truck stop for migrating great whites, then search for proof of a genetic connection between northern bull sharks and their cooler-climate cousins.

programme.title: Beasts of the Big Blue 1 - Snares Islands/ Tini Heke Ep1
programme.desc: Venture to the pristine wilderness of the Snares Islands, a remote animal sanctuary protected from the turbulent sea. Hop along with a colony of Snares crested penguins, soar with giant petrels and sooty shearwaters, and roar with giant sea lions.

programme.title: Beasts of the Big Blue 1 - Otago Peninsula/ Muaupoko Ep2
programme.desc: Set sail for New Zealands Otago Peninsula, a breeding refuge for endangered seabirds and marine mammals. Watch as sea lions, albatrosses, red-billed gulls, white-fronted terns, and fairy prions find mates, then nurture the next generation.

programme.title: Beasts of the Big Blue 1 - Top of the South/ Te Tau Ihu Ep3
programme.desc: Uncover a land of opposites atop New Zealands South Island, where one of the worlds longest sandbars attracts bar-tailed godwits and hungry pilot whales, and drowned river valleys provide a buffet for dusky dolphins and New Zealand fur seals.
